; Logan Wonnacott 11/11/2022
; The purpose of this code is to add together the positive numbers from a list of
; 10 random numbers
; Register 3 is my pointer register. This will point at a memory location to tell
; my program where to get the numbers from the given list
; Resigter 4 is my counter register. This will be decreased by 1 every loop
; Register 5 is my Sum Register. This is where the total value of the positive
; number will be kept
;Registers 6 is my Temporary Register. This is where I will store the value from
; the pointer and where I will check to see if this value is positive or negative

0011 0001 0000 0000 ; x3100 - starting address of the program

; The program description and code starts here

0101 101 101 1 00000; AND R5, R5, #0 (Initialize Sum [R5] to 0)
0101 100 100 1 00000; AND R4, R4, #0 (Initialize Counter [R4] to 0)
0001 100 100 1 01010; ADD R4, R4, #10 (Sets Counter [R4] to 10)
0101 110 110 1 00000; AND R6, R6, #0 (Initialize Temporary [R6] to 0)
0101 011 011 1 00000; AND R3, R3, #0 (Initialize Pointer [R3] to 0)
1110 011 0 0010 1011; LEA R3

0001 011 011 1 00001; ADD R3, R3, #1 (Increments pointer [R3])
0001 100 100 1 11111; ADD R4, R4, #-1 (Adds negative one to Counter [R4])
0000 100 000000100; BRz (Checks to see if Counter is negative)

0110 110 011 000000; LDR R6, R3, #0 (Loads R6 from number list)

0000 100 111111011; BRn R6 ____ (Checks to see if R6 is negative)

0001 101 101 000 110; ADD R5, R5, R6 (Adds Sum and R6)
0000 111 111111001; BRnzp (Loops back to [Pointer++])

1111 0000 0010 0101; Hault (Ends program)

; List of Numbers

